For using tricolor

```
import turtle
from anim import anim
col = ("orange","white","green")

t = turtle.Turtle()

screen = turtle.Screen()
screen.bgcolor("black")
tricolor(color)
```
For checking Internet
```
if internet_available():
    print("Internet is active")
else:
    print("Internet disconnected")

```
for getting time
```
x = zonetime('Asia/Kolkata')
print(x)
```

